  "detailed_description": "<br><br>In Vandalhalla you play to bring back amusement in a near future where fun is forbidden.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/37839234fefc1617a793665a9d383412.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br>You will bring back the fun in the city by participating in illegal fights. This fights highly recommends you to destroy the environment, kill your opponents and control capture points.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/579efdf0efbe16afa774f8debb87988d.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/579efdf0efbe16afa774f8debb87988d.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/579efdf0efbe16afa774f8debb87988d.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/3c26d594f9ee778b6a318925f8fc577a.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br>Vandalhalla give you a large panel of short, medium and long ranged weapons, grenades and diverse mechanics. Numerous classic and original abilities for always more interesting and chaotic battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/7d520b3a10c0c9d2cd0becc92738de07.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/7d520b3a10c0c9d2cd0becc92738de07.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/7d520b3a10c0c9d2cd0becc92738de07.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/ca035d51f78b2984bd33015d7d61d259.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=31 /></span><br><br>When you enter a battle you need to compose first a loadout with some weapons and abilities of the arsenal, then you are free.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/0a965065e68e57a045dc624b3752dc57.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/0a965065e68e57a045dc624b3752dc57.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/0a965065e68e57a045dc624b3752dc57.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Free to steal doors from building and killing opponents with it.<br>Free to catch missiles and send it back to the sender.<br>Free to become the weapon and throw yourself in a kamikaze style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/fd70763f5b5e8f394f5372ebb97eaa85.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br>Physical interaction is the key in Vandalhalla as you can see above, you can do whatever you with the help of your Gravity Gun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/615f67da7f643c805e7f28f8db1b303f.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=598 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/615f67da7f643c805e7f28f8db1b303f.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/615f67da7f643c805e7f28f8db1b303f.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br>In Vandalhalla you play to bring back amusement in a near future where fun is forbidden.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/37839234fefc1617a793665a9d383412.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br>You will bring back the fun in the city by participating in illegal fights. This fights highly recommends you to destroy the environment, kill your opponents and control capture points.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/579efdf0efbe16afa774f8debb87988d.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/579efdf0efbe16afa774f8debb87988d.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/579efdf0efbe16afa774f8debb87988d.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/3c26d594f9ee778b6a318925f8fc577a.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br>Vandalhalla give you a large panel of short, medium and long ranged weapons, grenades and diverse mechanics. Numerous classic and original abilities for always more interesting and chaotic battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/7d520b3a10c0c9d2cd0becc92738de07.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/7d520b3a10c0c9d2cd0becc92738de07.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/7d520b3a10c0c9d2cd0becc92738de07.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/ca035d51f78b2984bd33015d7d61d259.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=31 /></span><br><br>When you enter a battle you need to compose first a loadout with some weapons and abilities of the arsenal, then you are free.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/0a965065e68e57a045dc624b3752dc57.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/0a965065e68e57a045dc624b3752dc57.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/0a965065e68e57a045dc624b3752dc57.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Free to steal doors from building and killing opponents with it.<br>Free to catch missiles and send it back to the sender.<br>Free to become the weapon and throw yourself in a kamikaze style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/fd70763f5b5e8f394f5372ebb97eaa85.webp?t=1636052542\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br>Physical interaction is the key in Vandalhalla as you can see above, you can do whatever you with the help of your Gravity Gun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/615f67da7f643c805e7f28f8db1b303f.poster.avif?t=1636052542\" width=598 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/615f67da7f643c805e7f28f8db1b303f.webm?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662270/extras/615f67da7f643c805e7f28f8db1b303f.mp4?t=1636052542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
